Package: n4m
Type: Package
Title: Bindings to the N4M C ABI
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Gregory", family = "Beurier",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "beurier@cirad.fr"),
    person(given = "nirs4all-methods", family = "contributors",
           role = "ctb"))
Author: Gregory Beurier [aut, cre],
    nirs4all-methods contributors [ctb]
Maintainer: Gregory Beurier <beurier@cirad.fr>
Description: Thin R binding for the vendored nirs4all-methods C ABI (libn4m).
    Exposes a tier-1 .Call layer that dispatches into the 403 n4m_* symbols of
    the nirs4all-methods 1.9.0 ABI, plus an idiomatic tier-2 R API for 15
    operators commonly used in NIRS chemometrics: SNV, MSC, EMSC,
    SavitzkyGolay, FirstDerivative, SecondDerivative, ToAbsorbance,
    KubelkaMunk, Detrend, AsLS, AirPLS, KennardStone, SPXY, YOutlierFilter,
    and WaveletDenoise. The bindings produce bit-equivalent results to
    libn4m within the 1e-6 binding-parity tolerance (Gate 1).
License: CeCILL-2.1
